urce/Flag_of_Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Would Australian breakdancer B-Girl Raygun rather have not become an Olympian if she knew the trolling she'd be on the end of for achieving something that 99.9% of the world can only dream about?\", \"from\": 4930, \"to\": 5125, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4936, \"end\": 4946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9988494245286529, \"rank\": 0.0011450032619510146, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 4999, \"end\": 5007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999973674676, \"rank\": 2.6324001423985073e-09, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Besides, modern Olympic founder Pierre de Courbetin hated medal tables, a media invention that was banned by the Olympic Charter - and ignored by all - until just a few years ago.\", \"from\": 5127, \"to\": 5306, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics are a perfect ideal that are far from perfect and their guardians must reflect on their decision to allow convicted child rapist Steven van de Velde to compete and admit some accountability for the appalling treatment of boxer Khelif too.\", \"from\": 5308, \"to\": 5559, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5457, \"end\": 5469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"score\": 0.9999827886989401, \"rank\": 1.7211597299941707e-05, \"text\": \"van de Velde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \